---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Heading from '../components/heading.astro';
import Text from '../components/text.astro';
import Button from '../components/button.astro';
import bottles_drawing from '../img/bottles_drawing.svg';
import au_1 from '../img/au_1.webp';
import au_2 from '../img/au_2.webp';
import au_3 from '../img/au_3.webp';
import au_4 from '../img/au_4.webp';
import au_5 from '../img/au_5.webp';
import au_6 from '../img/au_6.webp';
import au_7 from '../img/au_7.webp';
import au_8 from '../img/au_8.webp';
import au_9 from '../img/au_9.webp';
import au_10 from '../img/au_10.webp';
import au_11 from '../img/au_11.webp';
---

<Layout title="About us">
  <main>

    <!-- section 1 -->
    <section class="w-full px-4 md:px-8 lg:px-12">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-245">

        <Heading type="h1" stylingclasses="text-center pt-12 pb-14 md:pt-16">
          ABOUT US
        </Heading>

        <Text>
          Belma is inspired by an unstoppable spirit, it’s a place for connection, laughter and memories. Cozy, lively and just the right touch of chaos. Sip, savor, and soak it all in.

          <br /><br />

          At Belma, we’re redefining what an all-day spot can be - making it just as inviting in the morning and midday as it is in the evening. We’re serving up the essentials all day long: craft beers, wines that speak for themselves, cocktails that surprise, and bites you’ll crave. Think crispy baguettes, melty sandwich grillé, artisanal baked goods and coffee that’s as bold as your plans.

          <br /><br />

          Whether you’re stopping by for a slow morning coffee, a laid-back lunch, or a lively night out, Belma is designed to draw you in at any hour.
          Our menu changes to keep things exciting, so follow us on →
          <a
            href="https://www.instagram.com/belma.1650/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-primary underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-secondary"
          >
            Instagram
          </a>
          to stay in the know.
        </Text>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- section 2 -->
    <section class="w-full">
      <div class="flex w-full justify-end">

        <img
          src={bottles_drawing.src}
          alt="Bottles drawing"
          class="w-full max-w-40 md:max-w-70 lg:max-w-85"
        />

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- section 3 MED GALLERI -->
    <section class="w-full py-14 md:py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-245">

        <div class="gallery-scroll flex gap-4 overflow-x-auto px-4 pb-5 md:gap-5 md:px-8 lg:px-12">

          <img
            src={au_1.src}
            alt="Belma gallery"
            class="h-60 w-48 shrink-0 object-cover md:h-80 md:w-64"
          />

          <img
            src={au_2.src}
            alt="Belma gallery"
            class="h-60 w-48 shrink-0 object-cover md:h-80 md:w-64"
          />

          <img
            src={au_3.src}
            alt="Belma gallery"
            class="h-60 w-48 shrink-0 object-cover md:h-80 md:w-64"
          />

          <img
            src={au_4.src}
            alt="Belma gallery"
            class="h-60 w-48 shrink-0 object-cover md:h-80 md:w-64"
          />

          <img
            src={au_5.src}
            alt="Belma gallery"
            class="h-60 w-48 shrink-0 object-cover md:h-80 md:w-64"
          />

          <img
            src={au_6.src}
            alt="Belma gallery"
            class="h-60 w-48 shrink-0 object-cover md:h-80 md:w-64"
          />

          <img
            src={au_7.src}
            alt="Belma gallery"
            class="h-60 w-48 shrink-0 object-cover md:h-80 md:w-64"
          />

          <img
            src={au_8.src}
            alt="Belma gallery"
            class="h-60 w-48 shrink-0 object-cover md:h-80 md:w-64"
          />

          <img
            src={au_9.src}
            alt="Belma gallery"
            class="h-60 w-48 shrink-0 object-cover md:h-80 md:w-64"
          />

          <img
            src={au_10.src}
            alt="Belma gallery"
            class="h-60 w-48 shrink-0 object-cover md:h-80 md:w-64"
          />

          <img
            src={au_11.src}
            alt="Belma gallery"
            class="h-60 w-48 shrink-0 object-cover md:h-80 md:w-64"
          />

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- section 4 -->
    <section class="w-full -mt-6 px-4 pb-32 md:mt-0 md:px-8 md:pb-40 lg:px-12 lg:pb-48">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-245">

        <Heading type="h2" stylingclasses="font-bold pt-5 pb-6">
          Work With Us at Belma
        </Heading>

        <Text>
          Belma is built on people, energy, and unforgettable moments. Behind every great coffee, cocktail, and guest experience is a team that brings the place to life every single day.
          We believe in creating a workplace that is just as welcoming and vibrant as the atmosphere our guests know us for.
          <br />
          A place where personality matters, teamwork is key, and no two days are ever the same.
          As we continue to grow, we’re always interested in meeting passionate people who would like to become part of the Belma journey.
        </Text>

        <Heading type="h3" stylingclasses="font-medium pt-5 pb-6">
          Curious about joining the team?
          <br />
          Explore career opportunities here.
        </Heading>

        <div class="flex justify-center pt-6 md:pt-0">

          <Button
            href="/were_hiring"
            variant="primary"
            stylingclasses="font-bold px-15"
          >
            READ MORE
          </Button>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>

<!-- style til scrollbar på galleriet -->
<style>
  .gallery-scroll {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
  }

  .gallery-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar {
    height: 6px;
  }

  .gallery-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
    background: transparent;
  }

  .gallery-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: 9999px;
  }
</style>